---
slug: "glossary"
permalink: "/es/glossary/index.html"
title: "Glossary: Brazilian terms in transfers | Morrison"
description: "NF-e, CNPJ, Pix, DPVAT, CNH, LGPD, BR-101/116 — what each means for passengers and finance teams."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Inicio", path: "/es/" }
  - { name: "Glossary", path: "/es/glossary/" }
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker reveal-up">Glossary</p>
    <h1 class="reveal-up">Brazilian terms<br>you'll run into.</h1>
    <p class="lead reveal-up">NF-e, CNPJ, Pix, DPVAT, CNH, LGPD — each in a single line.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <dl class="glossary-list">
      {%- for item in glossary.terms %}
      <div class="glossary-item">
        <dt><span class="glossary-term">{{ item.term }}</span></dt>
        <dd>{{ item.def.en }}</dd>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>Got your own term — tell us?</h2>
    <div class="cta-strip-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="mailto:{{ site.contacts.email }}">Email</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
